                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8475" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TEC-0126</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2839 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从模仿到国产化替代：东莞特澳的二次创新之路（微案例）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Imitation to Domestic Substitution: Dongguan Teao&#39;s Path of Secondary Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林海芬，杨瑞，左晓斌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东莞市特澳电子科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东莞特澳；后发型企业；二次创新；组织学习；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dongguan Teao; Follower Enterprise; Secondary Innovation; Organizational learning</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了东莞市特澳电子科技有限公司（以下简称：东莞特澳）的二次创新发展历程。东莞特澳通过简单模仿日本产品及工艺进入汽车阻尼器市场，后在尽可能保障产品关键性能的前提下，采用国内已有的原材料、部件，通过工艺创新完成产品的国产化替代，并根据国际风向不断更新自身技术，结合国内汽车阻尼器市场需求进行改进型创新，成为零部件方案提供商，由“边缘企业”逐渐发展成为汽车行业阻尼零部件重要供应商，得到全球多家权威机构和供应商的认可。本案例以时间轴为主线，通过案例描述的形式回顾了东莞特澳在汽车阻尼器行业的发展历程，旨在引导学员探索后发企业如何通过二次创新突破技术壁垒，追赶先发优势企业，实现本土替代的逻辑，并为我国后发零部件制造企业创新发展提供借鉴与启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study describes the secondary innovation development process of Dongguan Teao Electronics Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Dongguan Teao&quot;). Dongguan Teao entered the automotive damper market by simply imitating Japanese products and processes, and then, under the premise of guaranteeing the key performance of the products as much as possible, adopting the existing domestic raw materials and components, and completing the localization of the products through technological innovation to replace them, and constantly updating its technology according to the international winds and combining it with the domestic market demand for automotive damper to carry out improvement and innovation, and to become a parts and components solution provider. Teao has gradually developed from a &quot;marginal enterprise&quot; into an important supplier of damping components for the automotive industry, and has been recognized by a number of authoritative organizations and suppliers around the world. This case study, structured around a timeline, retrospectively reviews Dongguan Teao&#39;s development in the automotive damper industry. It aims to guide students in exploring how latecomer enterprises can break through technological barriers through secondary innovation, catch up with early-mover advantage enterprises, realize the logic of local substitution, and provide reference and inspiration for innovative development of latecomer component manufacturing companies in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2009</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》、《创新创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">二次创新；组织学习模式；技术追赶理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-08</td>
                            </tr>
